added.title: Wasted True Potential
added.description: In the wake of the previous season's victory, the ninja have gone soft and Master Wu must remind them of who they truly are.

added.title: Questing For Quests
added.description: Realizing they have gone soft, the ninja search for a quest to reignite their Spinjitzu training. Unfortunately, NINJAGO City is enjoying a period of rare tranquility.

added.title: A Rocky Start
added.description: The ninja have found their quest! Now they just have to get there, which involves a road trip through the Desert of Doom, a region supposedly inhabited by a giant scarab beetle.

added.title: The Belly of the Beast
added.description: To repair the Land-Bounty, the ninja must retrieve a critical engine component that has been swallowed by a giant scarab beetle.

added.title: Booby-Traps, and How To Survive Them
added.description: The ninja team up with a reluctant Clutch Powers to enter a mysterious pyramid where they inadvertently unleash an ancient evil.

added.title: Breakup
added.description:
Feeling left out, Adorabat wishes Mao Mao and Badgerclops would spend less time with each other and more time with her. When she gets
what she wishes for and accidentally breaks up their friendship, only the secret of their past can bring them back together.

added.title: Not Impressed
added.description: When a Sweetypie isn't impressed with the sheriff dept's antics, our three heroes try everything to win him over.

added.title: Enemy Mime
added.description: When the Sheriff's Dept fights a monster that copies their every move, they'll have to find a way to fight without fighting.

added.title: Outfoxed
added.description: When Rufus and Reg come to swindle the town, Sheriff Mao Mao teaches them a lesson in justice.

added.title: Bao Bao's Revenge
added.description: When Mao Mao's old partner threatens the kingdom, his friends will need to learn about his past in order to protect the present.

added.title: Fort Williams
added.description: When Craig can't go to the Creek, he and his mom decide to build the biggest blanket fort in the world!

added.title: The Other Side
added.description: Craig, Kelsey and JP must journey past the Overpass into uncharted territory, the Other Side of the Creek.

added.title: Summer Wish
added.description: When Craig decides to keep a lightning bug in a jar, he disrupts the delicate balance of Summer.

added.title: Turning the Tables
added.description: Craig dines at the restaurant where his older brother works and orders up a plate of REVENGE... and lots of breadsticks.

added.title: Kelsey the Author
added.description: Craig and Stacks help Kelsey become a real author turning her story into a book!

added.title: Unfriendly Competition
added.description: Aki must set aside a petty rivalry with Bert Wily in order to stop Chemistry Man from wreaking havoc at Silicon Central's Field Day.

added.title: Opposites Attract
added.description: Fire Man and Wave Man team up to evaporate the city's water supply, forcing Mega Man to team up with an ally of his own- Suna.

added.title: I.C.E. (In Case of Emergency)
added.description: When Ice Man decides to be a hero, Mega Man, influenced by Ice Man's literalness, steps down from the hero biz until a true crisis snaps him out of it.

added.title: Trust Your Guts, Man!
added.description: Guts Man tries to undo Dr. Light's eco-friendly disposal of trash in Silicon City by infiltrating the family and destroying the Lighthouse so he can eat it!

added.title: Drill of the Hunt
added.description: Mega Man tries a quick fix using Hypno Woman's powers to rehabilitate Drill Man, to disastrous results!

added.title: Blaze of Glory
added.description: Mega Man and Suna must overcome a sibling dispute over what to do on their day off in order to stop Fire Man from overheating the city.

added.title: Nice on Ice
added.description: An "unscheduled" TV appearance not only lands Aki in hot water for missing class, but sets Ice Man on a misguided mission to "unite" (i.e. freeze together) every human and robot couple in the city!

added.title: Hard Times in Silicon City
added.description: Mega Man must stop Blasto Woman from plundering the Museum of the Hard Age and its cache of military grade weaponry.

added.title: Tripping the Light Fantastic
added.description: Mega Man tries to save Dr. Light from a date with "Mari," who's actually Hypno Woman in disguise!

added.title: Running Wild
added.description: Student elections get blown out of proportion (literally) when Air Man lends his support to Aki's rival for class president, Peter Punk.

added.title: Sumo Goes West
added.description: Clarence learns his best friend Sumo may transfer to another school! It's up to Clarence to protest, petition and rally to convince everyone to let Sumo stay - or face losing his closest school pal!

added.title: Rock Show
added.description: Chad's band Dogmon, plays a show for the first time in years, giving Clarence and Mary a chance to really rock out.

added.title: Stump Brothers
added.description: After Clarence and Sumo cause a power outage in Sumo's family home, they're sent off in the hot desert with Sumo's older brother to retrieve a generator part. Will they survive the trek or will Sumo's sibling rivalry boil over?

added.title: Man of the House
added.description: Clarence's first night home alone spirals out of control, forcing Clarence and his pals to wage war against their own home security measures.

added.title: La Melancolia de Oscar y Erizo
added.description: Susie organiza el concurso anual de talentos, y todos los campistas compiten para ganar.

added.title: Sintiendose Especiales
added.description: Oscar y Erizo llegan a una planeta que no tiene emociones.

added.title: Fantasma, El Nino
added.description: Oscar y Erizo se hacen amigos de un fantasma que no recuerda quién es.

added.title: Vampiro de Computadora
added.description: Oscar encuentra un videojuego viejo y misterioso en la biblioteca.

added.title: Cronicas de Mentiras Basquetboleras
added.description: Con la ayuda de Basketball, Oscar hace un tiro impresionante que le permite conseguir un lugar en la Liga Dorada.

added.title: Enemigo Mimo
added.description: Cuando el departamento del sheriff se enfrenta a un monstruo que copia todos los movimientos, tendrán que encontrar el modo de pelear sin pelear.

added.title: La Venganza de Bao Bao
added.description: Cuando el antiguo compañero de Mao Mao amenaza al reino, los amigos de Mao Mao tendrán que conocer su pasado para proteger el presente.

added.title: Separacion
added.description: Adorabat siente que es dejada de lado y desea que Mao Mao y Colosal pasen menos tiempo juntos y más tiempo con ella. Pero cuando el deseo de Adorabat se hace realidad y destruye la amistad de Mao Mao y Colosal, solo el secreto de su pasado podrá volver a unirlos.

added.title: No Me Impresiona
added.description: Cuando un Corazoncito no se siente impresionado con las hazañas del departamento del sheriff, nuestros tres héroes intentan de todo para conquistarlo.

added.title: Superado
added.description: Cuando Rufus y Reg llegan para engañar al pueblo, el sheriff Mao Mao les enseña una lección sobre la justicia.
